This paper deals with the security and analysis of Android applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of static program analysis, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the analysis, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
